@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 120
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam padding 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 13

actor "User" as AUser

rectangle "Traffic Camera Browser" {
  boundary "Browsing History UI" as UI
  control "History Controller" as HC
  entity "HistoryEntry" as HE
  entity "User" as UserEntity
  entity "Camera" as CameraEntity
}

AUser --> UI : open history / clear history
UI --> HC : history request
HC --> UserEntity : identify user

HC --> HE : retrieve/clear history items
HC --> CameraEntity : load camera details
HC --> UI : show updated history

note bottom of UI
After logging in, a browsing history button
appears. Users can view or clear history.
end note
@enduml